                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card__side card__side--back card__side--back-1">
                            <div class="card__cta">
                                <div class="card__price-box">
                                    <p class="card__price-only">Only</p>
                                    <p class="card__price-value">$399</p>
                                </div>
                                <a href="#popup" class="btn btn--white">Sign up now!</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="col-1-of-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__side card__side--front">
                            <div class="card__picture card__picture--2">
                                &nbsp;
                            </div>
                            <h4 id="card__heading">
                                <span class="card__heading-span card__heading-span--2">Pro Package</span>
                            </h4>
                            <div class="card__details">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>only 14.90$ / meal</li>
                                    <li>1 meal 10 days/month</li>
                                    <li>Order 24/7</li>
                                    <li>Access to newest creations</li>
                                    <li>Free delivery</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card__side card__side--back card__side--back-2">
                            <div class="card__cta">
                                <div class="card__price-box">
                                    <p class="card__price-only">Only</p>
                                    <p class="card__price-value">$149</p>
                                </div>
                                <a href="#popup" class="btn btn--white">Sign up now!</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="col-1-of-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card__side card__side--front">
                            <div class="card__picture card__picture--3">
                                &nbsp;
                            </div>
                            <h4 id="card__heading">
                                <span class="card__heading-span card__heading-span--3">Starter Package</span>
                            </h4>
                            <div class="card__details">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>19$ / meal</li>
                                    <li>1 meal</li>
                                    <li>Order from 8 am to 12 pm</li>
                                    <li>&nbsp;</li>
                                    <li>Free delivery</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card__side card__side--back card__side--back-3">
                            <div class="card__cta">
                                <div class="card__price-box">
                                    <p class="card__price-only">Only</p>
                                    <p class="card__price-value">$19 per meal</p>
                                </div>
                                <a href="#popup" class="btn btn--white">Sign up now!</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    
        </section>
    
        <section class="section-stories">
            <div class="bg-video">
                <video class="bg-video__content" autoplay muted loop>
                    <source src="img/video.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                    Your browser is not supported!
                </video>
            </div>
            <div class="u-center-text u-margin-bottom-big">
                <h2 class="heading-secondary" style="margin-top: -.5em;">
                    We make people genuinely happy
                </h2>
            </div>
    
            <div class="row">
                <div class="story">
                    <figure class="story__shape">
    
                        <img srcset="img/cust-8.jpg 400w, img/cust-8.jpg 2000w"
                            sizes="(max-width: 56.25em) 13vw, (max-width: 37.5em) 20vw, 180px" alt="Customer eating a meal"
                            class="story__img" src="../img/cust-8.jpg">
    
                        <figcaption class="story__caption">
                            An Na
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
    
                    <div class="story__text">
                        <h3 class="heading-tetiary u-margin-bottom-small">
                            I had the best week ever with my family
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            CravedFoods is just awesome! I just launched a startup which leaves me with no time for cooking,
                            so CravedFoods is a life-saver. Now that I got used to it, I couldn't live without my daily
                            meals!. Inexpensive, healthy and great-tasting meals, delivered right to my home.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="row">
                <div class="story">
                    <figure class="story__shape">
    
                        <img srcset="img/cust-9.jpg 400w, img/cust-9.jpg 2000w"
                            sizes="(max-width: 56.25em) 13vw, (max-width: 37.5em) 20vw, 180px" alt="Person on a tour"
                            class="story__img" src="img/cust-9.jpg">
    
                        <figcaption class="story__caption">
                            Kabi Li
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
    
                    <div class="story__text">
                        <h3 class="heading-tetiary u-margin-bottom-small">
                            WOW! My life is completely different now
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            I was looking for a quick and easy food delivery service in Shenzhen. I tried a lot of them and
                            ended up with CravedFoods. Best food delivery service in the Bay Area. Keep up the great work!.
                            We have lots of food delivery here in Zhanjiang, but no one comes even close to CravedFoods. Me
                            and my family are so in love!.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    
            <div class="u-center-text u-margin-top-huge">
                <a href="/api/user/allfeedbacks" class="btn-text">Read all stories &rarr;</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    
        <section class="section-book js--section-order">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="book">
                    <div class="book__form">
                        <div class="container">
                            <% if(error && error.length > 0){ %>
                                <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                                    <%= error %>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                            <% if(success && success.length > 0){ %>
                                <div class="alert alert-success" role="alert">
                                    <%= success %>
                                </div>
                            <% } %>
                        </div> 
                        <form action="/api/user/login" method="post" class="form">
                            <div class="u-margin-bottom-medium">
                                <h2 class="heading-secondary">
                                    Start Ordering Now
                                </h2>
                            </div>
    
                            <div class="form__group">
                                <input type="text" class="form__input" placeholder="Username" id="name" name="username" required>
                                <label for="name" class="form__label">Username</label>
                            </div>
    
                            <div class="form__group">
                                <input type="password" name="Password" class="form__input" placeholder="Password" id="email" required>
                                <label for="email" class="form__label">Password</label>
                            </div>
    
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <div class="form__radio-group u-margin-bottom-medium">
                                    <input type="radio" class="form__radio-input" id="small" name="size">
                                    <label for="small" class="form__radio-label">
                                        <span class="form__radio-button"></span>
                                        Order for self
                                    </label>
                                </div>
    
                                <div class="form__radio-group">
                                    <input type="radio" class="form__radio-input" id="large" name="size">
                                    <label for="large" class="form__radio-label">
                                        <span class="form__radio-button"></span>
                                        Order for friend
                                    </label>
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-group">
                                    <button type="submit " class="btn btn--orange">Next step &rarr;</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    
